{"tid":2459222,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸抗爭｜7歲女童在家遭槍擊 死於父親懷中 19歲兄長遭毒打後被捕","createTime":"2021-03-24T04:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T15:42:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":180,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"ce05068cbe53284cfc522b7ed98f092dca74ca66","tid":2459222,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"緬甸中部城市曼德勒近日不斷發生軍警血腥鎮壓事件，7歲女童欽苗奇（Ma Khin Myo Chit）周二在寓所被士兵射殺。當地居民表示，事發時警員和士兵向街頭圍觀的市民開槍，遇害女童則是在軍方搜屋時遭槍擊身亡，她的19歲兄長亦被軍方毒打及帶走。<br />\n<br />\n曼德勒周二共有3人被軍警殺害，令全國自2月初軍方發動政變後的死亡人數增至260人。緬甸軍方近日持續在曼德勒市中心附近的昌妙達齊（Chanmyathazi）區鎮壓示威，清走民眾設置的路障，又多次向人群開槍。<br />\n<br />\n軍警周二清場時再次向街上眾人開槍，遇害女童欽苗奇一家當日下午被士兵登門搜查，更有士兵向她開槍，欽苗奇最後死於父親懷中，她的兄長亦被捕。從網上流傳照片可見，年僅7歲的欽苗奇滿身是血，腹部可見有傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210324/OOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210324%2FOOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE%2F&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2FuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=b4d5a4fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210324%2FOOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE%2F&h=616f4f46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210324/OOJGNXCKKZFC3FNSV3SFRHZ7JE/</a>"},{"pid":"e69b182f997a11f6e8a79f7235a587a9ed36da2f","tid":2459222,"uid":271497,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0721b4633df9312cbf2c272a58a5d7273ba2584f","tid":2459222,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3ce67bb729ef740a64e1985b326f5fece110bd","tid":2459222,"uid":279333,"like":0,